Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,《法外情真》前情回顾\N{\fs12}Previously on The Guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.88,0:00:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能再酗酒了  尼古拉斯\N{\fs12}You can't drink any more Nicolas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.76,0:00:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能再嗑药\N{\fs12}You can't use drugs,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不能再\N{\fs12}and you can not continue to lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.14,0:00:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,对你爱的人说谎了\N{\fs12}to the people who love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.62,0:00:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,露露我向你求婚了\N{\fs12}Lulu I asked you to marry me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而你却看着我  好像我在侮辱你\N{\fs12}and you just looked at me like I was insulting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你和苏珊娜·佩尔上床的原因吗\N{\fs12}So you screwed Susanne Pell?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,露露求你了\N{\fs12}Lulu please...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,别走\N{\fs12}Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  你嗑了什么\N{\fs12}Nike, what did you take?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要帮助\N{\fs12}You need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你得做出改变了\N{\fs12}You gonna make some changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉我们在接下来的一个月都需要门诊治疗\N{\fs12}My feeling is we should start outpatient for the next 30 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快点  - 我来了\N{\fs12}- Come on! - I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.64,0:00:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心  我会赶上的\N{\fs12}Don't worry. I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 尼克  - 上午好  阿尔文\N{\fs12}- Nick. - Morning, Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我住哪里\N{\fs12}You know where I live?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.82,0:00:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  嗯  是的\N{\fs12}Yeah. Um, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.86,0:00:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我有段时间没见你了\N{\fs12}I haven't seen you around for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  露露  她不想让我去律所\N{\fs12}Well, you know, Lulu-- she doesn't really want me around the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你要坐公共汽车吗\N{\fs12}You catch the bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一周三天  我必须要减少燃料的使用\N{\fs12}Three days a week. Gotta cut down on those fossil fuels.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真有你的  是啊\N{\fs12}Good for you. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直看着这些  呃  混合动力汽车\N{\fs12}I've been looking at those, uh, hybrid cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.30,0:01:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,也许到期限满的时候\N{\fs12}Maybe when the lease runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我的公交车到了\N{\fs12}Well, here's my bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  阿尔文  你有时间可以谈一谈吗  - 我要迟到了  尼克\N{\fs12}-Hey, Alvin, do you have a minute to talk? -I'm gonna be late, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我正在努力弥补  你知道的   那个项目\N{\fs12}Well, I'm working on my amends for the-- you know, the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文  你上车吗\N{\fs12}You coming, Alvin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不了  克利姆\N{\fs12}Not today, Clim.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.66,0:01:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  诺拉\N{\fs12}Hi, Norah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.24,0:01:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  谢谢\N{\fs12}Thanks. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.66,0:01:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,第九步已经开始了  是吗\N{\fs12}The ninth step already, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我正在努力\N{\fs12}l-- I'm working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.72,0:01:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还挺快的\N{\fs12}That's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.60,0:01:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我写了一些东西  然后  呃\N{\fs12}I wrote some things down, and, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,外面太冷了  尼克\N{\fs12}lt's pretty cold out here, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以开车送你去上班  然后我们可以在车里聊一聊\N{\fs12}I'll give you a ride to work, and we can do it in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以\N{\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.19,0:01:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  尼克  我很欣赏你所说的一切\N{\fs12}Look, I appreciate everything you've been saying, Nick,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  我很乐意过去的就让它过去  但是\N{\fs12}and, of course, I'm happy to let bygones be bygones, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.62,0:01:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我已经做了三个星期了  而这只是一个30天的项目\N{\fs12}Well, I'm three weeks in. It's only a 30-day program.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  要知道  以我的情况\N{\fs12}Well, you see, in my situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.03,0:02:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,将近一年的时间里  我都没有做好补偿的准备\N{\fs12}I wasn't ready to make my amends for almost a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  阿尔文\N{\fs12}Well, Alvin...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那好吧  - 对啊  对啊\N{\fs12}- Okay, then. - Right. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,请进\N{\fs12}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 尼克  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Nick. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你最近怎么样\N{\fs12}How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,还好  你好吗\N{\fs12}Okay. How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,还可以  你收到我的留言了吗\N{\fs12}Okay. Did you get my messages?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  是的  我还是觉得你应该继续\N{\fs12}Yeah. Yeah, I still think that you should continue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,接受治疗在接案子之前\N{\fs12}with your outpatient therapy before you take cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我打电话不是为了这个  - 因为  我想  直到我知道\N{\fs12}- I wasn't calling about that. - Because, I think, until I know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有喝酒或吸毒\N{\fs12}that you're not drinking or doing drugs,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我让你在这里做律师是极不负责任的\N{\fs12}it would be highly irresponsible for me to let you practice law here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我打电话不是为了律所的事\N{\fs12}I wasn't calling about the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.93,0:02:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs12}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我打电话是因为  呃\N{\fs12}I was calling because, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和你谈谈我做过的事\N{\fs12}I wanted to talk to you about what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我怀了我们的孩子\N{\fs12}About the fact that I'm pregnant with our child,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你却和另一个女人做爱的事儿吗\N{\fs12}and you're having sex with another woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,也许现在不是最好的时机\N{\fs12}Maybe this isn't the best time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,也许不是\N{\fs12}Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,也许  嗯  下次吧\N{\fs12}Maybe, uh, another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  出车祸了\N{\fs12}Nick, it crashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吗  - 那辆公交车  它出事了\N{\fs12}- What? - The bus. It crashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哪一辆公交车  - 我要坐的那辆公交车  - 38号公交车\N{\fs12}- What bus? - My bus-- the 38B.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,冲出了51号公路上的护栏\N{\fs12}Went over a guardrail on Route 51 .
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,新闻报道说  很多人都死了\N{\fs12}The news is saying that a lot of people are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来是要上车的\N{\fs12}I was just about to get on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来应该在那辆公共汽车上\N{\fs12}I was supposed to be on that bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这事儿我们得抢占先机  呃  派特  - 很好\N{\fs12}- We'll stay ahead of this, uh, Pat. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克已经在协调公关了\N{\fs12}Jake is already coordinating with the-- your PR--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今天要制定悲伤咨询计划\N{\fs12}We're setting up a grief counseling plan today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在将会有民事诉讼出现\N{\fs12}- Now, there will be civil suits filed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  我们的答案是全面否定所有索赔和责任\N{\fs12}Our answer, of course, will be a blanket denial of all claims and liability.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,司机给警察提供了血液和尿液样本\N{\fs12}The driver's given blood and urine samples to the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在和他的女儿一起在县医院\N{\fs12}and he's down at the county hospital right now with his daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  呃  他已经同意今天晚些时候和我们谈谈\N{\fs12}but, uh, he has agreed to speak with us later today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去采访那个司机\N{\fs12}I'll interview the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不  杰克会处理的\N{\fs12}No. Jake's taking care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以采访的\N{\fs12}I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,请注意  它不会是\N{\fs12}Be advised. It won't be a--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不  让杰克来处理\N{\fs12}No. Jake's on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们确实需要  呃  公共汽车上的维修记录\N{\fs12}But we do need, uh, maintenance records on the bus,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,还有司机的驾驶手册\N{\fs12}and, uh, the regulation manual for your drivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,悲惨的阿勒格尼县过境公交车事故\N{\fs12}...tragic AIlegheny County Transit bus crash
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在5号公路已经有5人死亡\N{\fs12}on Route 5S has reached S5.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡人数正在攀升\N{\fs12}The death toll has climbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  让我们开始工作吧\N{\fs12}Well, let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我稍后再和你谈  好吗？\N{\fs12}I'll talk to you later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以和司机去交涉\N{\fs12}I can talk to the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也许你可以顺便去一下交通部门\N{\fs12}I thought maybe you could, uh, drop over to the Transit Authority
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,检查一下事故重建工作\N{\fs12}and check on that accident reconstruction work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我可以在去司机家的路上这么做\N{\fs12}Well, I could do that on the way to the driver's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,尼古拉斯  这个案子可能会让阿勒格尼损失数千万美元\N{\fs12}Nicholas, this case could cost Allegheny Transit tens of millions of dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他们需要我们保持连贯性和一致性\N{\fs12}What they need from us is continuity and consistency.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说  这案子我不能插手吗\N{\fs12}You're saying I can't work on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  跟我进来一下\N{\fs12}Well, come on in here a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,尼古拉斯  你现在有很多其他的事情要处理\N{\fs12}Nicholas, you've got a lot of important stuff going on right now for yourself--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须得工作\N{\fs12}I gotta work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 爸爸  我能应付的  - 好吧\N{\fs12}- Dad, I can handle working. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在去司机家的路上  我会到交通局去\N{\fs12}I will stop by the Transit Authority on the way to the driver's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗\N{\fs12}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,请进\N{\fs12}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一个新的委托人  他只有13岁\N{\fs12}I got a new client. He's 13,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他的父亲在今天的公交车事故里去世了\N{\fs12}and his father died today in that bus accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫康纳·亚当斯  他也在公共汽车上\N{\fs12}His name is Connor Adams. He was on the bus, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他受伤了吗\N{\fs12}Was he hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他的手腕受伤了  他缝了几针  但除此之外\N{\fs12}His wrist. He's got some stitches, but otherwise--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我能为你做些什么\N{\fs12}Well, what can I do for you?
