Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.78,0:22:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.29,0:22:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我想露露可能需要一些帮助  嗯  考虑到你的特殊性\N{\fs12}You know, I think Lulu may need some help, uh, understanding your particularities.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,例如  她的父亲  我看见那个人了  对吧\N{\fs12}For instance, her father. I saw that guy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.64,0:22:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他酗酒成性\N{\fs12}Had alcoholic written all over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显 她是看着一个瘾君子长大的\N{\fs12}Clearly she grew up watching somebody enable an addict.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白我的意思吗  - 没有\N{\fs12}- Know what I mean? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.03,0:22:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这个孩子的父亲在车祸中丧生\N{\fs12}So, this kid whose dad died in the crash,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:22:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,今天在法庭上  在达姆森法官面前\N{\fs12}in court today, in front of Judge Damsen--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.08,0:22:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,苏珊娜和露露给他找了寄养家庭\N{\fs12}Suzanne and Lulu bring in this foster family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:22:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲是白人  母亲是黑人\N{\fs12}Dad's white, mom's black.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.17,0:22:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这个孩子  在法庭前  说了那个单词\N{\fs12}This kid, in front of the court, says the N word.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.09,0:23:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,拒绝去寄养家庭\N{\fs12}Refuses to go with the foster family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.98,0:23:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他全家都是白人至上主义者\N{\fs12}His whole family's, like, these white supremacists.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.22,0:23:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他父亲去世了很难过  但是  嗯  伙计\N{\fs12}Sad story about the dad dying, but, uh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.72,0:23:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我也认识他的父亲\N{\fs12}I knew the father, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,从公交车上\N{\fs12}from the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.40,0:23:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,从没见过那个孩子  但是\N{\fs12}Never saw the kid, but, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.96,0:23:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他父亲以前叫那个司机的名字时\N{\fs12}the dad used to call that, uh, driver names
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.13,0:23:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,总是很小声\N{\fs12}all the time, under his breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那个司机  克利姆 是个好人\N{\fs12}The driver, Clim-- good man--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.91,0:23:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他总是直直地盯着前方  开着公交车\N{\fs12}just used to stare straight ahead and drive that bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.56,0:23:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嗨\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你爸爸在吗  - 没有  只有奶奶在家\N{\fs12}- Is your daddy here? - No. Just Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.04,0:23:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是诺拉  对吧\N{\fs12}lt's-- It's Norah, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.64,0:23:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是尼克  我昨天来过\N{\fs12}I'm Nick. l-- I came around yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.30,0:23:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说  呃  公车上可能有人不太友好\N{\fs12}I heard that there, uh, might've been someone on the bus that wasn't very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.56,0:24:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.16,0:24:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道你是否记得\N{\fs12}I was wondering if you remember
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你爸爸有和其他人相处得不好\N{\fs12}if your dad was having a-- a bad time with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,也许不是昨天  也许  也许  也许是另一天\N{\fs12}Maybe not yesterday, maybe-- maybe-- maybe another day?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.34,0:24:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候  有个男人会对爸爸说些事情\N{\fs12}This man, some days, would say things to Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.98,0:24:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什么样的事情\N{\fs12}What kind of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.77,0:24:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,辱骂他\N{\fs12}Call him bad names.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.37,0:24:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.13,0:24:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸总是告诉我不要听\N{\fs12}Daddy always told me not to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.78,0:24:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他说那种话不应该听\N{\fs12}He said that kind of stum shouldn't be listened to.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.67,0:24:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  这是对的  你爸爸是对的\N{\fs12}Oh, that's right. Your daddy's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.95,0:24:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人对你爸爸很刻薄\N{\fs12}This man that was mean to your daddy,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.10,0:24:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,车撞毁的时候他在车上吗\N{\fs12}was-- was he on the bus when it crashed?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.54,0:24:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  谢谢你  诺拉\N{\fs12}Okay. Thanks, Norah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.97,0:24:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他儿子叫我黑鬼\N{\fs12}His son called me a nigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.52,0:24:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他什么时候说的\N{\fs12}When did he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.73,0:24:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在车撞毁之前\N{\fs12}Before we crashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.84,0:24:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸转过身来\N{\fs12}Daddy turned around.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.63,0:25:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他真的很生气\N{\fs12}He was really mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.32,0:25:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他转过身来  对着那个孩子和爸爸大喊\N{\fs12}He turned around and yelled at the kid and his dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.55,0:25:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,事情就是这样发生的\N{\fs12}and that's when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.06,0:25:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  露露  我想事情就这样了\N{\fs12}So, I think that's everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.67,0:25:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我回头再跟你说  好吧  再见  亲爱的\N{\fs12}I'll talk to you about it later. Okay. Bye, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.13,0:25:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  发生了什么事\N{\fs12}Oh. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.31,0:25:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,康纳和其他孩子相处得不太好\N{\fs12}Connor's not exactly getting along with the other kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.02,0:25:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,\N{\fs12}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.62,0:25:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  坐下来  康纳\N{\fs12}Okay, have a seat, Connor.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.65,0:25:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你想告诉我发生了什么事吗\N{\fs12}You want to tell me what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.80,0:25:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你想告诉我发生了什么事吗\N{\fs12}You want to tell me what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.98,0:25:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,康纳\N{\fs12}Connor?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.33,0:25:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这对你来说一定是非常困难的时刻\N{\fs12}You know, I know this must be an extremely difficult time for you--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.45,0:25:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸的葬礼在星期五\N{\fs12}My dad's funeral is on Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.29,0:25:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我知道你一定很爱你爸爸\N{\fs12}All right. You know, I know that you must have loved your dad a lot--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.39,0:25:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别谈论我的父亲  - 不，我只是说\N{\fs12}- Don't talk about my father. - No, I just mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.18,0:26:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要谈论我的父亲\N{\fs12}Don't talk about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.54,0:26:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果坚信你父亲相信的东西\N{\fs12}lf you keep believing the things that your father believed
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.33,0:26:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,也继续这样行事  你就会失去一切的\N{\fs12}and you keep acting the way that you act, you're gonna lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.08,0:26:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你会失去每一个出现在你面前的机会的\N{\fs12}You will lose every opportunity that comes your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.63,0:26:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没人会想要你的  康纳\N{\fs12}No one will want you, Connor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.52,0:26:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.59,0:26:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人会的\N{\fs12}Nobody will.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.63,0:26:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你昨晚来过我家\N{\fs12}Understand you stopped by the house last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.99,0:26:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你和诺拉谈过了\N{\fs12}Understand you spoke to Norah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.77,0:26:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她告诉你的是真的\N{\fs12}What she told you was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.98,0:26:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的  我当时没看路\N{\fs12}lt's true. I wasn't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.47,0:26:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  坐下来\N{\fs12}Um, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.61,0:26:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs12}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.49,0:26:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  克利姆  呃  你前几天说过  嗯\N{\fs12}Uh, Clim, uh, you said the other day that, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.29,0:27:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你在冰上行驶时踩刹车\N{\fs12}if you'd hit the brakes when you were going over the ice
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.82,0:27:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你仍然会失去对公交车的控制\N{\fs12}that you still would have lost control of the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.52,0:27:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.54,0:27:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过你没有超速\N{\fs12}You said that you weren't exceeding the speed limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.81,0:27:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.35,0:27:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你也没有鲁莽驾驶\N{\fs12}And you weren't driving recklessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.82,0:27:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,对的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.81,0:27:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,再给你一次机会你会改变什么\N{\fs12}Would you have done anything differently?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.85,0:27:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我把目光从路上移开\N{\fs12}I looked away from the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.42,0:27:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我转向那个人  对他大喊\N{\fs12}I turned to the man, and I yelled at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.16,0:27:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,克利姆  如果你把这次事故归咎于自己\N{\fs12}Clim, if-- if you blame yourself for this accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.13,0:27:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,公交车公司会和你撇清关系的\N{\fs12}the bus company will distance itself from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.82,0:27:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,过失杀人罪可能会受到刑事指控\N{\fs12}There may be criminal charges filed for negligent homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.42,0:27:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白这是什么意思吗\N{\fs12}You understand what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.22,0:27:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  这可能是个意外\N{\fs12}I mean, this could have been an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.45,0:27:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这不一定是你的错\N{\fs12}It doesn't have to be your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.46,0:27:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们说一点不一样的\N{\fs12}Let's say I say things different.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.25,0:27:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这对诺拉意味着什么\N{\fs12}What does that mean for Norah?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.74,0:28:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我说我没有看别处\N{\fs12}I say I didn't look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.37,0:28:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她不得不说同样的话  对吧\N{\fs12}She has to say the same thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.43,0:28:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对吗\N{\fs12}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.02,0:28:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人  几个月前\N{\fs12}This guy, a few months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.62,0:28:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,上了公交车  但是他没有车费\N{\fs12}gets on the bus, and he don't have the fare.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.50,0:28:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉他  他得付钱才能乘车\N{\fs12}I tell him he gotta pay to ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.26,0:28:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫我放过他一次  因为我以前也见过他\N{\fs12}He tells me to give him a break because I seen him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.01,0:28:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉他我不能那样做\N{\fs12}I tell him I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.66,0:28:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他叫我\N{\fs12}So he calls me--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.15,0:28:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫我黑鬼\N{\fs12}he calls me a nigger,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.81,0:28:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,然后下车了\N{\fs12}and he gets off the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.88,0:28:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天早上  他上了车\N{\fs12}The next morning, he gets on,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.67,0:28:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他就坐在我后面\N{\fs12}and he sits down right behind me,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.45,0:28:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,然后开始骂我\N{\fs12}and he starts with the names,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.78,0:28:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,从卡内基一直到纽约一直说\N{\fs12}and he keeps it up all the way from Carnegie into the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.49,0:28:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,而我只能听他说\N{\fs12}And I just listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.89,0:28:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,试着想象他不在那里\N{\fs12}Try to imagine that he's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.87,0:29:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,做好我的本职工作\N{\fs12}Just do my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.80,0:29:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,事发当天\N{\fs12}Day it happened--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.04,0:29:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有暴风雪\N{\fs12}snowstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.25,0:29:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的学校都不上课\N{\fs12}All the schools were closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.90,0:29:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因此  我让我的女儿诺拉和我一起乘车\N{\fs12}I had my daughter, Norah, riding with me on account of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.13,0:29:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这个男人和他的儿子上了公共汽车\N{\fs12}This man gets on the bus with his boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.17,0:29:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就坐在我旁边\N{\fs12}They sit down close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.85,0:29:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我听见他在窃窃私语\N{\fs12}I hear him whispering.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.59,0:29:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他开始跟我说话\N{\fs12}He started saying things to me
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.99,0:29:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,当着他儿子的面  当着我女儿的面\N{\fs12}in front of his boy, in front of my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.63,0:29:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了看我的女儿  她在盯着地板看\N{\fs12}I look at my daughter. She's staring at the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.77,0:29:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我在考虑是否要停车\N{\fs12}I try to think whether to stop the bus or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.59,0:29:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我想还是不了\N{\fs12}l-- I think no.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.23,0:29:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在山上行驶\N{\fs12}So, we drive over the hill, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.72,0:29:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这时  我听到\N{\fs12}And that's when I hear it--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.94,0:29:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他的儿子\N{\fs12}his boy
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.64,0:29:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我的宝贝\N{\fs12}calling my baby
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.79,0:29:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,黑鬼\N{\fs12}a nigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.74,0:30:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我的宝贝那个词\N{\fs12}Calling my baby that word.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.87,0:30:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我转向那个人和他的孩子\N{\fs12}I turned to that man and his child
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.39,0:30:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,把我要对他说的话告诉了他\N{\fs12}and I tell him what I tell him,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.50,0:30:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来\N{\fs12}and the next thing I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.44,0:30:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,公交车\N{\fs12}the bus...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.34,0:30:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来我知道的是\N{\fs12}The next thing I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.33,0:30:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道\N{\fs12}You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.23,0:30:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有做好我的本职工作\N{\fs12}I turned away from my job.
