Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.39,0:40:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我正要走  我待会再跟你说\N{\fs12}Nope. I was just leaving. I'll talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.12,0:41:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天早上给我打电话了\N{\fs12}You called this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.80,0:41:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  请坐\N{\fs12}Yeah. Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.23,0:41:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你可以重新开始接案子了\N{\fs12}I think it's okay for you to start taking cases again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.43,0:41:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.24,0:41:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  嗯  有个人\N{\fs12}Right. So, uh, there's a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.83,0:41:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫阿尔弗雷德·金斯顿\N{\fs12}His name is Alfred Kingston.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.13,0:41:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  他被误判了强奸罪\N{\fs12}Um, he was wrongfully convicted of rape,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.60,0:41:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他被判了十年监禁\N{\fs12}and he served ten years of a hundred-year sentence
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.42,0:41:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在DNA测试证明他无罪之前\N{\fs12}before the DNA test cleared him of the charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.21,0:41:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.33,0:41:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他想要儿子的监护权  但问题在于他的妻子\N{\fs12}He wants custody of his son, but the problem is the wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.63,0:41:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,她有点激动  而阿尔弗雷德在想他怎么才能要回他的孩子\N{\fs12}She's kind of moved on, and Alfred's just wondering how he's gonna get his kid back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.09,0:41:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  明白了  谢谢你\N{\fs12}Okay. Got it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.75,0:41:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他在外面等你\N{\fs12}He's waiting for you outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.69,0:42:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,金斯顿先生  尼克·福林\N{\fs12}Mr. Kingston? Nick Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.64,0:42:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道你是清白的  - 是的\N{\fs12}- I understand you were exonerated. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.78,0:42:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\fs12}Come with me.
